          </form>
        
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panels-container">
        <div class="panel left-panel">
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Hush kelbsiz !</h3>
            <p>
Najot ta'lim CRM tizimga hush kelibsiz !
Bizda o’z sohasining mutaxassislari faoliyat olib borishadi. Sizni o’z safimizda ko’rishdan mamnun bo’lamiz.

            </p>
          </div>
          <img src="http://localhost:9000/image/Najot_Talim-01.png" class="image" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
